data.text:
Prince Luitpold and Princess Beatrix of Bavaria, Prince Rasso and his wife Theresa of Bavaria, Prince Leopold and his wife Ursula of Bavaria (R-L) attend the memorial service in Berg am Starnberger See, Germany, 13 June 2011. 125 years ago, Ludwig II of Bavaria drowned and was found close to the chapel. Photo: Tobias Hase (ATTENTION!! Use for current coverage only!)
